summary: WHILE ATTEMPTING TO BACK OUT OF MY GARAGE THE REAR AUTOMATIC EMERGENCY BRAKING ENGAGED. THERE IS NO REASON IT SHOULD HAVE ENGAGED, IT WAS DARK OUT BUT NOTHING WAS AROUND. I HAVE DISABLED THE AUTOMATIC EMERGENCY BRAKING SYSTEM OPTION BUT I SHOULD NOT HAVE TO WORRY ABOUT MY CAR I HAVE OWNED FOR 45 DAYS DOING THIS.
